@node maxpro "MAX's BBS Professional - The future of BBS's!"

There are 3 versions of MAX's BBS Professional available...

v1.00	- PD evaluation copy - Crashes at midnight
v1.66	- Registered ONLY..  New look, cleaner & faster than v1.00
v2.00	- Look below at the feature list!

                  MAX's BBS Professional features list :)

Already in MAX's Pro v2.00

True Os2.04/os3.x screens & windows  (interleaved under os3.x)
All screens are named public ones.  Format:  MAXsBBS?  where ? is the node 
	number!
New look gadgets
Very FAST!  Uses under 4% CPU time on a slow 030 :)  0.60% when idle!
Script based File_id/.readme/$Ver: file detection
Banner adding/stripping, virus checking & credit docking :)
Free Download support
New 250 line message editor! :)
New MAX's commands!
Altered Paragon protocol.  Doors won't lock up on 2+ local logins!
Before/After mail import scripts for Freq servers, traptoss etc etc.
ANSI/RIP support
Screen colour locking on os3.0 - Stops hisoft basic doors screwing things up!
Animated login intro :)
Advanced door port structure
Ami-Express door emulation!!!  Run LSD-Wall on MAX's pro :))))))


Being added before release...

Trapdoor/GMS/Telnet Spawnable
Plug-in support..  External progs can become part of max's!



Current project size:	approx 7,000 lines pure asm
			     + 2,000 lines asm in config editor!
			     

The file handler is THE most powerful available for ANY BBS system!!!!!!

Even supports colour file_id's!!!..  Also checks the file format so you
can add a script to nuke imcomplete pictures for example! :) Or limit
virus checking to certain file types..  The list is endless :)


